Package hr.fer.zemris.java.fractals

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComplexFactory
    Factory class that objects of Complex, ComplexPolynomial and ComplexRootedPolynomial classes.
    DaemonicThreadFactory
    Factory method used for creating daemon threads.
    FractalProducerImpl
    IFractalProducer implementation that produces fractals with Newton-Raphson method.
    FractalProducerImpl.Job
    Job to be given to working threads.
    Newton
    Program that calculates and shows a fractal in a window.
    NewtonRaphsonCalculator
    Contains methods for calculating fractals with the Nuewton-Raphson method.
